                                            And those who envied will say, ‚ÄúWe knew you would be great.‚Äù
                                            But you will smile‚Äînot with pride‚Äîbut with gratitude. Because you refused to stay stuck.
                                            
                                            You broke out.
                                            And that, my friend, is the envy of those who never tried.
